\intbl \ql \b Summary of Evaluator Report\b0 \line The evaluator indicated that the representation of the Independent Institute of Education to the reasons given for non accreditation does not address any of the core issues raised. The design and structure of the course are still found not to be in line with the national educational objectives as well as with the profession. To simply change the name of the programme to bypass the responsibilities towards the students and the profession does not resolve the glaring shortcomings of the programme. Those include aspects like the course structure\'2C staffing\'2C  library resources and teaching strategy.\line The Directorate concurs with the recommendation that the decision not to accredit the programme be upheld for the reasons cited in the first report.  \cell \pard 

